response.overview: DEAD MEDIA is the story of a troubled young woman, her aging hipster uncle, a haunted DVD, and a movie night that canâ€™t die.  The film stars Sammi-Jack Martincak (Shameless, The Rookie, I Love You Phillip Morris), James Urbaniak (The Fabelmans, Oppenheimer, The Venture Bros), Sam Landman (Good Sport), and Anna Sundberg (Fargo) with a cameo from Bill Corbett (RiffTrax, MST3K).  The film also features luminaries of the Minnesota film and theater community Jessica Fenton, John Middleton, Antonio Teodoro, Natalie Rae Wass, Jacob Mullan, Rob Ward, Gael Palen, Audrey Parker, Andrew Stecker, Sulia Rose Altenberg, Rachel Buhman, Shanan Custer, Jim Robinson, Tim Uren, Joseph Scrimshaw, Sara Scrimshaw, and Nissa Nordland.
